  "detailed_description": "New Supper Banana! is a funny adventure platformer. And it's drawn entirely in a notebook!<br><br><strong>Features:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>10 Levels<br></li><li>Hand-drawn graphics<br></li><li>A funny story<br></li><li>Customizable difficulty: You can choose the amount of hearts you have</li></ul><br>---------------------------------------------------------<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The world is in danger</h2>The Mad Eater has appeared and is eating everyone. You have to save them!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1681080/extras/7e68248f54a11291386ab014a3b11df7.poster.avif?t=1769351568\" width=638 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1681080/extras/7e68248f54a11291386ab014a3b11df7.webm?t=1769351568\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1681080/extras/7e68248f54a11291386ab014a3b11df7.mp4?t=1769351568\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Use Supper Dash!</h2>Thankfully, you are awesome and have a special move: Supper Dash!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1681080/extras/14b4f98bc2a3ba00e9b0b4571236cc7e.poster.avif?t=1769351568\" width=534 height=222 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1681080/extras/14b4f98bc2a3ba00e9b0b4571236cc7e.webm?t=1769351568\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1681080/extras/14b4f98bc2a3ba00e9b0b4571236cc7e.mp4?t=1769351568\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Funny story</h2>Enjoy a funny and surprisingly epic story with Supper Banana and his friends.<b